entries.journal_entry_completion_summary: you have located the lost Corsec patrol and reported back to Lieutenant Varias.
entries.journal_entry_description: A group of Corsec agents was sent ahead to scout out the factory, however, they have yet to report back. Lieutenant Varias has asked you to look for them.
entries.task00_journal_entry_description: Lieutenant Varias has lost contact with a patrol of Corsec agents. He wants you to locate the patrol.
entries.task01_journal_entry_description: you have found the lost Corsec patrol, report back to Lieutenant Varias.
